            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further</p><p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>Mediterranean veg</strong></p>",
